_sText:
Hey this is my first DeathRun map.
The map has 6 Bonus Granades and 14 Traps.

Map has 55CT spawns and 2 T spawns.

The Traps:

01. Noob Box
02. Spiked Up
03. Rotating Floor ( 2*Z-Axis - 2*Z-Axis-Reverse )
04. Smoking Kills
05. Don't play with Fire
06. Elevator of Death
07. LaserZ of Doom
08. The Cutting Edge
09. Rotating Floor ( 1*X-Axis - 1*Y-Axis )
10. Hammer Fall
11. Radioactive Bomb-Barrels
12. 5* 50/50 Chance
13. Flying Saws
14. Ventilation
